{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":9,"day":30}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席和人民在一起","authors":["郭沫若侯波"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"总路线万岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌路线力争先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限光明照大千。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁高呼三脱帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两番跃进再加鞭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啀啀桀犬吠尧日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翩翩鸳凰颂舜天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂百花齐放蕊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年建设胜千年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大跃进万岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民解放力空前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片东风奏凯旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引水上山山下水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀天抚地地摩天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万千公社翻禾浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小高炉涌铁泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化尽昆仑巅上雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要将戈壁化良田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社万岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一大二公岂可忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创新宇宙控玄黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按劳分配权三级，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐业欢虞颂万章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有纪有纲工易化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗涝抗旱力难量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最高功业归于党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旭日光华照八方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1959年9月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和韶山学校的学生们在一起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和济南市东郊人民公社社员握手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新华社记者 侯 波摄"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}